data.description:
Nicely maintained, move-in ready 2/1 Home with two additional detached 24 x 24 buildings being used as workshops. All buildings are concrete block construction with metal roofs. Home upgraded with new windows and roof replacement in 2023. Electrical service upgraded in 2024 to 200 AMP W/Generator Outlet. Home recently connected to Central Water and the 500’ deep well w/5” casing is still in operation. HVAC and ductwork are newer and Septic drainage field replacement in 2022.
Additionally, NO HOA, 7 minutes’ drive to beautiful Lake Letta public boat ramp (2.7 miles), and Dollar General is within walking distance (0.2 Miles). Being sold AS/IS with right to inspection. Property is a must see to appreciate the serenity!
